Welcome to the Fall 2022 Calgary AfterSchool at Thornhill Aquatic& Recreation Centre! Calgary AfterSchool Program: Calgary AfterSchool is a city-wide initiative that offers youth positive, constructive activities after school, which ultimately helps build stronger and safer communities for youth to develop into successful adults, all while following current Alberta Health Services COVID-19 protocols. After school programs provide benefits for children and youth that include:
  • Lower stress levels for working parents (know where their children are and what they are doing).
  • Increased recreation opportunities.
  • More opportunities to develop social, physical, leadership and creative skills.
Cost: FREE • During program hours, facility access and program instruction are free to those who want to participate.
